snippet.title: Alice is Dead HD Trailer
snippet.description:
This is just a little trailer showing some of the updated art, nothing here is final though and there is so much more than what this video shows! Please wishlist the game if you want to support it! Thanks for looking! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1826770/Alice_is_Dead_Hearts_and_Diamonds/

Captions by Erasmus_Magnus
